preference.name: VisualReportDefinition_OpenByName_ColumnPreferences
preference.preference_description: Specifies the columns to be displayed for the dialog "Open By Name" for Visual Report Definitions. The format for valid values is "TypeName.PropertyName", where "TypeName" is the Visual Report Definition internal name (VisualReportDefinition) and "PropertyName" is the internal name of the property to be displayed.
